name: #30- Golden cold bath
description:
There are some actions in life that are universal, no matter where we are, who we are or what we eat; at the end we all go alone and face our naked butt...

Gouache and charcoal on Fabriano paper, digitized, manicured, enhanced, placed into an environment and situation in Photoshop. 112 frames in loop, 1024px square. About 39hs involved in the process.
